fooddata.title: Black Chana(Usal) With Thepla
fooddata.description: Protein packed black chana dal cooked in roasted coconut & curry leaf gravy. Served with 3 Theplas. Topped with Coriander. Allergen information: Contains Gluten.

fooddata.title: Kadhai Paneer, Bhindi, Paratha Thali
fooddata.description: Enjoy scoops of soft whole wheat paratha with flavourful kadhai paneer and bhindi chana. Served with salad and pickle. Allergen information: Gluten, dairy, nuts, seeds.

fooddata.title: Lasooni Methi Paneer, Aloo Gobhi & Paratha Thali
fooddata.description: Tangy, spicy, juicy mix of chana masala has been paired with delicious roasted potatoes cooked with methi leaves and fresh peas and soft whole wheat parathas. Served with salad & pickle. Allergen information: Gluten.

fooddata.title: Kadhai Paneer, Soya Masala Sabzi, Paratha Thali
fooddata.description: A flavourful paratha thali! Enjoy scoops of soft whole wheat paratha with flavourful kadhai paneer and chewy tasty soya masala sabzi. Served with salad and pickle. Allergen information: Gluten, dairy, nuts, seeds, soy.
